      • Credentials

        public Credentials(java.lang.String userName,
                   java.lang.String passPhrase,
                   java.lang.String domain,
                   java.lang.String workstation)
        Create user/passPhrase credentials for NTLM proxy authentication. This form is only used when accessing the service through a proxy using the NTLM scheme.
        Parameters:
        userName - The user name (e-mail address) for the authenticating user
        passPhrase - The passPhrase for the authenticating user
        domain - The domain to be authenticated against
        workstation - The name of the workstation
        Since:
        1.3.1
